                        "game-obj": "Traits",
                        "game-id": "ea42ab3d3aa3a6b9843571bb3f28e689",
                        "text": "An olfactory effect can affect only creatures that can smell it. This applies only to olfactory parts of the effect, as determined by the GM.",
                        "classes": [
                            "sense"
                        ]
                    }
                ],
                "text": "10 feet. A creature entering the aura or starting its turn in the aura must succeed at a DC 26 Fortitude save or become <a aonid=\"34\" game-obj=\"Conditions\">sickened 1</a> plus, on a critical failure, <a aonid=\"35\" game-obj=\"Conditions\">slowed 1</a> as long as it's sickened). While within the aura, the creature takes a \u20132 circumstance penalty to saves against disease and to recover from the sickened condition. A creature that succeeds at its save is temporarily immune for 1 minute."
            }
